The paper discusses the design of energy-efficient sensory embedded systems with inference capabilities, which involves topics related to embedded systems, computer vision, machine learning, and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.ET (Embedded Systems), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AR (Augmented Reality), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
